Anonymous;;2011;;PG-13;;Drama,Thriller;;6.9;;Roland Emmerich;;Rhys Ifans,Vanessa Redgrave,David Thewlis,Sebastian Armesto,Rafe Spall,Edward Hogg,Xavier Samuel,Sam Reid,Jamie Campbell Bower,Joely Richardson,Paolo De Vita,Trystan Gravelle,Robert Emms,Tony Way,Julian Bleach,Derek Jacobi,Alex Hassell,James Garnon;;Anonymous is a political thriller which also involves the question of who actually wrote the plays of William Shakespeare. It follows Edward de Vere, 17th Earl of Oxford (<a href="/name/nm0406975/">Rhys Ifans</a>), and is set against the backdrop of the succession of Queen Elizabeth I (<a href="/name/nm0000603/">Vanessa Redgrave</a>) and the Essex Rebellion against her.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt1521197/